01:06:01,540 --> 01:06:02,917
SALA STAMPA

1274
01:06:14,971 --> 01:06:18,140
Morti, Dispersi

1275
01:06:18,224 --> 01:06:24,772
GANG-HO JOO

1276
01:06:48,671 --> 01:06:49,547
Pronto?

1277
01:06:51,007 --> 01:06:52,008
Pronto?

1278
01:06:54,051 --> 01:06:55,136
Seo-u?

1279
01:06:56,095 --> 01:06:58,097
